1. Button
2. Crypted partition
- Install LUKS:
yum install cryptsetup-luks
- Gen keyfile:
dd if=/dev/random of=/mnt/usbstick/keyfile bs=1 count=256
- End crypt them:
gpg -c /mnt/usbstick/keyfile
- Init crypted partition:

cryptsetup luksFormat --key-file /mnt/usbstick/keyfile /dev/sdc2
gpg -o - keyfile.gpg | cryptsetup luksFormat /dev/sdc2 -

- Link DM:

cryptsetup --key-file ~/tmp/keyfile luksOpen /dev/sdc2 cryptfs
gpg -o - /mnt/usbstick/keyfile.gpg | cryptsetup --key-file - luksOpen /dev/sdc2 cryptfs

- Format FS:
mkfs.ext2 /dev/mapper/cryptfs
- Mount:

mkdir /mnt/cryptfs
mount /dev/mapper/cryptfs /mnt/cryptfs
====
* Connect crypted partition:
gpg -o - /mnt/usbstick/keyfile.gpg | cryptsetup --key-file - luksOpen /dev/sdc2 cryptfs && mount /dev/mapper/cryptfs /mnt/cryptfs
* Disconnect:
umount -f -l /mnt/cryptfs && cryptsetup luksClose /dev/mapper/cryptfs
== Full ==
* Connect:
mount /dev/sde1 /mnt/usbstick && gpg -o - /mnt/usbstick/keyfile.gpg | cryptsetup --key-file - luksOpen /dev/sdc2 cryptfs && mount /dev/mapper/cryptfs /mnt/cryptfs && service postgresql start
